      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec driver, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been properly addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings to maintain torsional rigidity. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end remain within tight tolerances. Finished with a well-damped suspension setup for optimal turn-in, this M3 offers the raw mechanical feedback and linear power delivery synonymous with the golden era of M-division engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
